room_title: Escape room "The Pirate's Den" by MagIQ Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 1446 S Robertson Blvd, Los Angeles, CA 90035
room_description: The world’s been looking for the lost treasures of the most famous pirate, Henry Morgan for nearly 400 years. From 1676, Morgan retired from piracy, performed vice-gubernatorial duties in Jamaica, managed his estate – and drank like a fish. You’ll have to fight numerous hardships and challenges through your expedition! If you succeed, you’ll gain a worthy reward and be part of unimaginable wealth!
